<p><em>Pictured above is the source of the domain sugerplum.uk</em></p>
<p>Welcome, this is my server. I am <strong>Aiden Ross</strong>, a student of computer science and mathematics at <strong>Appalachian State University</strong>. At the time of writing this I have been working on and off on this server for about <em>~1.5 months</em>.</p>
</section>
<section id="purpose" class="level2">
